sources.title: Return To Earth
sources.description: Sci-fi movie from Macau. In 2500 Earth is almost destroyed by a big bang, humanity is forced to evacuate. 2565 Earth is back but not as it use too. Three astronauts are sent to Earths core to investigate. Starring: Johan Karlberg , Lily Ge , Angela Lao , Xie Yun Kun , Rika Kishida.

metadata.Plot: A cinematic mountain-bike film. Featuring some of the sports biggest athletes. The ninth feature from award-winning adventure filmmakers Anthill Films. Return to Earth proves that when we lose track of time, we can make the most of it.
metadata.Director: Colin Jones, Darren McCullough, Darcy Wittenburg
metadata.Writer: Ian Dunn, Colin Jones, Darren McCullough
metadata.Actors: Reed Boggs, Casey Brown, Thomas Genon
